    "created_at": "2017-05-16T10:52:06Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-05-16T10:52:06Z",
    "body": "This is not a regression, the default behavior of fetch api with file scheme is same as chrome. Although the spec supports file scheme, there is no guidelines. Hence explicit support was avoided. You can add fetch support to file scheme in your app by using [webFrame.registerURLSchemeAsPrivileged](https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/docs/api/web-frame.md#webframeregisterurlschemeasprivilegedscheme-options) api. I would also recommend to avoid setting privileges to file scheme and instead create a custom protocol that is privileged. Closing this out, thanks!"
  },
