    "created_at": "2017-05-16T13:13:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-05-16T13:13:46Z",
    "body": "@deepak1556 Shouldn't both requests fail?  In Chrome, both requests fail due to the same origin policy unless you pass `--disable-web-security`.  However, in electron the XMLHttpRequest request works without setting `webPreferences.webSecurity` to false."
