    "created_at": "2017-05-16T15:02:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-05-16T15:02:18Z",
    "body": "@vossad01 yeah that's because XHR and fetch have different CORS checking paths and we have allowed request to any origin succeed from file scheme. As you suggest the behavior should be consistent for both but changing it now will break apps, we can streamline this in 2.0. In the meantime we can document the behavior of file scheme and promote the use of custom protocols."
